text: (puok poutatbot) kadauchchea shai t nder nowpel del vea niyeay towkean mnoussa tha chaur anak brachheang( nung a l laoh) choh . haey nowpel delke ban brachheang vea bercha niyeay tha pitabrakd nasa khnhom min peakpnth cheamuoy anak laey . pitabrakd nasa khnhom khlach a l laoh del chea mcheasa krobkrong piphp teangoasa
